## Keyword Research Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define seed keywords and topics
- [ ] 2. Generate keyword ideas using tools and logic
- [ ] 3. Analyze search volume and competition
- [ ] 4. Categorize by intent (informational, navigational, transactional)
- [ ] 5. Group into topic clusters
- [ ] 6. Prioritize by opportunity and fit

